# Node dependencies — never commit. Run `npm install` to regenerate.
node_modules/

# Generated native projects.
# DEV DECISION: `npx cap add ios` and `npx cap add android` generate the ios/ and
# android/ folders. You decide whether to commit them:
#   - COMMIT them if you hand-edit native config (Info.plist, entitlements, icons,
#     Gradle, signing) and want it version-controlled (common for app projects).
#   - IGNORE them (uncomment the two lines below) if you treat them as fully
#     regenerable from this config and manage native settings another way.
# ios/
# android/
